Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.64,0:00:07.92,2,,0,0,0,,Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.56,0:00:09.88,2,,0,0,0,,Fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.31,0:00:11.68,2,,0,0,0,,Air.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.04,0:00:13.52,2,,0,0,0,,Water.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.21,0:00:18.83,2,,0,0,0,,Only the Avatar can master all four elements
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.21,0:00:21.01,2,,0,0,0,,and bring balance to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.64,0:00:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,土强
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.56,0:00:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,火烈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.31,0:00:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,气和
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.04,0:00:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,水善
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.21,0:00:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,只有神通能掌握所有四种元素
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.21,0:00:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,并为世界带来平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.12,0:00:28.25,2,,0,0,0,,Bolin's a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.47,0:00:31.76,2,,0,0,0,,The mover star stopped Varrick's kidnapping attempt on president Raiko,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.86,0:00:33.27,2,,0,0,0,,proving his brother's innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.59,0:00:37.27,2,,0,0,0,,Mako and Korra were reunited, but Korra has no memory of their breakup.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.58,0:00:40.50,2,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, Jinora's spirit is still trapped in the spirit world,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.50,0:00:42.97,2,,0,0,0,,and Tonraq and his southern forces have been defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.25,0:00:47.02,2,,0,0,0,,Now it's up to team Avatar to stop Unalaq before harmonic convergence.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.12,0:00:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,波林成了英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.47,0:00:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这位电影明星阻止了瓦里克绑架雷鼓总统
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.86,0:00:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,证明了他哥哥是无罪的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.59,0:00:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,信和科拉重聚，但科拉忘记了分手的事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.58,0:00:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,同时，吉诺拉的魂魄仍然被困在灵界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.50,0:00:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,托纳克和他的南方部队已经被打败了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.25,0:00:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,现在只有神通小队能在谐波汇聚之前阻止吴纳克
