Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.94,0:01:28.98,2,,0,0,0,,What's up with the coat?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.88,0:01:31.20,2,,0,0,0,,And where did you get that pie?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.06,0:01:34.54,2,,0,0,0,,It's a Varrick ship. You never know what you're gonna find.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.90,0:01:37.20,2,,0,0,0,,There's a whole level filled with funhouse mirrors.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.32,0:01:39.71,2,,0,0,0,,Of course, there's also the cat-gator deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.98,0:01:43.19,2,,0,0,0,,I miss that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.43,0:01:45.80,2,,0,0,0,,He really knew how to make a long trip interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.25,0:01:48.09,2,,0,0,0,,So have you told Korra yet about how
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.25,0:01:49.09,2,,0,0,0,,you guys broke up 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.09,0:01:52.41,2,,0,0,0,,and then you kind of started dating Asami while she was off getting attacked by dark spirits?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.77,0:01:53.78,2,,0,0,0,,You wanna keep it down?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.19,0:01:56.05,2,,0,0,0,,I'm waiting for the right moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.53,0:01:57.87,2,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mako.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.23,0:02:01.29,2,,0,0,0,,You know, a wise man once told me that delivering bad news to a girlfriend
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.38,0:02:05.50,2,,0,0,0,,was like ripping off a blood-sucking leech. You just have to do it fast and get it over with.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.09,0:02:08.44,2,,0,0,0,,I hate it when you listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.08,0:02:09.60,2,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.44,0:02:11.60,2,,0,0,0,,Unalaq will be waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.02,0:02:14.27,2,,0,0,0,,You'll need all of your Avatar power to stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.76,0:02:16.49,2,,0,0,0,,I'm going to close the spirit portals,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.61,0:02:19.11,2,,0,0,0,,lock Vaatu in for another 10,000 years,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.11,0:02:21.66,2,,0,0,0,,and make Unalaq wish he'd never been born!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.14,0:02:35.73,2,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Mako.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.24,0:02:40.26,2,,0,0,0,,Did you want something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.35,0:02:42.75,2,,0,0,0,,Uh, no, no, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.16,0:02:51.48,2,,0,0,0,,As soon as we reach the Southern water tribe,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.78,0:02:53.87,2,,0,0,0,,we'll blast through the blockade at the main port.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.27,0:02:56.59,2,,0,0,0,,Then we can rendezvous with Tonraq and his troops,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.91,0:03:00.45,2,,0,0,0,,crash through the defenses around the portal, and enter the spirit world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.84,0:03:05.02,2,,0,0,0,,Whoa, since when does my little brother want to crash or blast through anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.44,0:03:07.68,2,,0,0,0,,I'll do whatever it takes to save my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.21,0:03:10.07,2,,0,0,0,,We all want to save Jinora,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.44,0:03:12.98,2,,0,0,0,,but I think your plan might be a tad overaggressive,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.45,0:03:15.70,2,,0,0,0,,seeing as there are only seven of us and one ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.04,0:03:16.41,2,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.13,0:03:18.18,2,,0,0,0,,And what do you suggest?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.29,0:03:20.75,2,,0,0,0,,An attack like this calls for strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.46,0:03:25.33,2,,0,0,0,,I remember when I was surrounded by pirates in the hurricane straits.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.97,0:03:27.53,2,,0,0,0,,We managed to capture them all
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.80,0:03:30.97,2,,0,0,0,,with just a feather, two eggs, and a barrel of molasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.97,0:03:33.61,2,,0,0,0,,I don't want to hear any of your crazy stories now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.61,0:03:34.62,2,,0,0,0,,This is serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.19,0:03:38.99,2,,0,0,0,,Are we almost there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.33,0:03:40.01,2,,0,0,0,,Almost.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.75,0:03:40.98,2,,0,0,0,,But
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.66,0:03:44.33,2,,0,0,0,,I just picked up a distress signal from the Southern troops.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.97,0:03:45.82,2,,0,0,0,,There's a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.30,0:04:00.91,2,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.78,0:04:05.20,2,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.86,0:04:06.50,2,,0,0,0,,Where's dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.89,0:04:10.57,2,,0,0,0,,Unalaq wiped out the entire Southern resistance
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.63,0:04:11.87,2,,0,0,0,,and captured your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.19,0:04:14.27,2,,0,0,0,,I'll get him back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.28,0:04:16.09,2,,0,0,0,,Where is my mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.19,0:04:18.18,2,,0,0,0,,She's in the healing hut.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.74,0:04:20.38,2,,0,0,0,,So many injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.41,0:04:34.24,2,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.53,0:04:36.74,2,,0,0,0,,Her soul is trapped in the spirit world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.08,0:04:37.98,2,,0,0,0,,Oh, my goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.70,0:04:39.98,2,,0,0,0,,How long has she been away?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.49,0:04:41.48,2,,0,0,0,,Almost a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.04,0:04:43.68,2,,0,0,0,,I've tried to keep her energy flowing,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.89,0:04:45.46,2,,0,0,0,,but I can feel her slipping away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.92,0:04:47.79,2,,0,0,0,,You're the only one who can help her now, mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.54,0:04:59.48,2,,0,0,0,,How much longer can she survive like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.01,0:05:00.63,2,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.40,0:05:04.05,2,,0,0,0,,But she's very strong to have lasted this long.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.37,0:05:08.32,2,,0,0,0,,I talked to the rebels.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.61,0:05:10.85,2,,0,0,0,,They said Unalaq's got the Southern portal surrounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.56,0:05:13.62,2,,0,0,0,,Harmonic convergence is only a few hours away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.86,0:05:17.28,2,,0,0,0,,Then we have to break through the enemy lines ourselves and get to the portal now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.86,0:05:19.28,2,,0,0,0,,There's no use in talking anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.42,0:05:20.61,2,,0,0,0,,We know what our mission is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.13,0:05:22.61,2,,0,0,0,,A suicide mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.39,0:05:26.61,2,,0,0,0,,You know, I was in a similar situation once.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.97,0:05:30.35,2,,0,0,0,,My platoon had crawled through the desert with no water for a week,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.71,0:05:34.20,2,,0,0,0,,but when we finally located the only oasis for 100 Miles,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.50,0:05:37.16,2,,0,0,0,,it was surrounded by angry sandbenders.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.53,0:05:40.50,2,,0,0,0,,I realized our only chance to get to the water
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.80,0:05:42.78,2,,0,0,0,,was to drop in from above.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.24,0:05:45.01,2,,0,0,0,,So I fashioned together a catapult,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.25,0:05:47.79,2,,0,0,0,,and with the help of a few well-trained hog-monkeys...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.85,0:05:49.67,2,,0,0,0,,enough of your ridiculous lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.98,0:05:52.71,2,,0,0,0,,Can't you see that the fate of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.74,0:05:54.37,2,,0,0,0,,and Jinora's life depends on what we do here today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.95,0:05:57.58,2,,0,0,0,,Hold on. Maybe Bumi's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.21,0:06:00.06,2,,0,0,0,,We don't have a catapult and hog-monkeys,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.06,0:06:02.84,2,,0,0,0,,but we have a flying bison, and there's a plane on Varrick's ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.60,0:06:05.16,2,,0,0,0,,Maybe we can attack from above.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.52,0:06:06.14,2,,0,0,0,,What are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.58,0:06:11.27,2,,0,0,0,,Mako, Bolin, and I can use the plane to create a distraction and scatter some of the defenses.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.34,0:06:15.85,2,,0,0,0,,You, Tenzin, Bumi, and Kya can fly into the spirit portal on Oogi when you see an opening.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.44,0:06:18.23,2,,0,0,0,,Let's get moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.83,0:06:39.55,2,,0,0,0,,What are we still doing here, father?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.24,0:06:42.91,2,,0,0,0,,The invasion was completely successful,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.91,0:06:44.64,2,,0,0,0,,and the Southern tribe is under our control.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.41,0:06:46.88,2,,0,0,0,,The spirit portals are open.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.33,0:06:48.50,2,,0,0,0,,You've restored balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.00,0:06:50.04,2,,0,0,0,,Now we would like to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.87,0:06:52.21,2,,0,0,0,,You don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.92,0:06:57.69,2,,0,0,0,,Everything I've achieved so far will pale in comparison with what I'm about to accomplish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.15,0:07:00.87,2,,0,0,0,,What else is there? The water tribe is united.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.27,0:07:03.51,2,,0,0,0,,After today, there will be no more water tribe,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.95,0:07:05.51,2,,0,0,0,,no more nations of any kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.37,0:07:10.63,2,,0,0,0,,The world is about to be transformed into something magnificent and new,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.49,0:07:13.74,2,,0,0,0,,and I will lead this glorious revolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.73,0:07:18.76,2,,0,0,0,,Now go outside and get the troops ready to defend the spirit portal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.96,0:07:19.88,2,,0,0,0,,From whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.35,0:07:21.88,2,,0,0,0,,We've already beaten everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.27,0:07:23.72,2,,0,0,0,,The Avatar will be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.37,0:07:25.59,2,,0,0,0,,She has no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.02,0:07:41.82,2,,0,0,0,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.23,0:07:46.37,2,,0,0,0,,I'm an earthbender strapped to the wing of a plane hundreds of feet in the air,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.37,0:07:48.02,2,,0,0,0,,so no.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.38,0:07:51.63,2,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. There's no way they'll be expecting this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.26,0:08:02.90,2,,0,0,0,,I think they were expecting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.82,0:08:32.03,2,,0,0,0,,Asami!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.66,0:08:34.55,2,,0,0,0,,Get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.78,0:08:44.41,2,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.57,0:09:15.95,2,,0,0,0,,There are spirits everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.46,0:09:17.52,2,,0,0,0,,I don't see an opening.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.26,0:09:21.12,2,,0,0,0,,Let's circle around and see if we can find a way in from the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.02,0:09:25.60,2,,0,0,0,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.38,0:09:45.14,2,,0,0,0,,The spirits are weighing Oogi down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.14,0:09:46.42,2,,0,0,0,,We're losing altitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.00,0:09:50.06,2,,0,0,0,,Get off of him, you sticky, nasty, little blob of goo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.58,0:09:54.87,2,,0,0,0,,If I go, you're coming with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.87,0:09:58.52,2,,0,0,0,,Bumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.84,0:10:35.91,2,,0,0,0,,I wish Varrick was filming this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.15,0:10:38.98,2,,0,0,0,,We could call it <i>Nuktuk: Sky warrior.</i>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.96,0:10:57.24,2,,0,0,0,,Brace yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.92,0:11:35.45,2,,0,0,0,,Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.02,0:11:39.40,2,,0,0,0,,Korra,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.53,0:11:41.76,2,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.47,0:11:43.37,2,,0,0,0,,I failed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.73,0:11:45.37,2,,0,0,0,,Don't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.08,0:11:48.02,2,,0,0,0,,Harmonic convergence isn't here yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.71,0:11:50.02,2,,0,0,0,,We still have a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.63,0:11:58.35,2,,0,0,0,,We tried.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.65,0:12:01.15,2,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.76,0:12:06.32,2,,0,0,0,,You've all got front-row seats for the beginning of the new world order.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.94,0:12:08.82,2,,0,0,0,,You don't know what you're doing, Unalaq.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.54,0:12:11.55,2,,0,0,0,,Freeing Vaatu won't make you powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.55,0:12:16.11,2,,0,0,0,,It will only make you a traitor to everything good that's happened for the last 10,000 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.75,0:12:18.92,2,,0,0,0,,You think what Avatar Wan did was good?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.57,0:12:21.72,2,,0,0,0,,Driving almost all the spirits from this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.44,0:12:25.20,2,,0,0,0,,The Avatar hasn't brought balance, only chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.06,0:12:28.85,2,,0,0,0,,You call yourself the bridge between the two worlds,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.10,0:12:30.51,2,,0,0,0,,but there shouldn't be a bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.72,0:12:32.18,2,,0,0,0,,We should live together as one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.62,0:12:34.16,2,,0,0,0,,Even if Vaatu escapes,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.77,0:12:36.64,2,,0,0,0,,I'll put him right back in his prison,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.03,0:12:38.03,2,,0,0,0,,just like Wan did.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.49,0:12:42.41,2,,0,0,0,,It's true that, when Wan fused with Raava, he tipped the scales in her favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.08,0:12:45.65,2,,0,0,0,,But this time, I'll be here to level the playing field.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.37,0:12:50.01,2,,0,0,0,,When harmonic convergence comes, I will fuse with Vaatu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.96,0:12:53.25,2,,0,0,0,,And together, we will become the new Avatar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.00,0:12:55.68,2,,0,0,0,,A dark Avatar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.79,0:12:58.55,2,,0,0,0,,Your era is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.41,0:13:01.20,2,,0,0,0,,Think about what you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.11,0:13:05.45,2,,0,0,0,,I know that you've always had a deep connection with the spirits,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.16,0:13:07.82,2,,0,0,0,,but you're still a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.74,0:13:09.97,2,,0,0,0,,You're still my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.70,0:13:12.77,2,,0,0,0,,You're Eska and Desna's father.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.15,0:13:17.15,2,,0,0,0,,Are you willing to throw your humanity away to become a monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.56,0:13:19.98,2,,0,0,0,,I'll be no more of a monster than your own daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.71,0:13:24.76,2,,0,0,0,,The only difference is that, while she can barely recognize her own spiritual power,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.07,0:13:27.30,2,,0,0,0,,I will be in complete alignment with mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.81,0:13:29.40,2,,0,0,0,,Vaatu and I will be as one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.01,0:13:32.60,2,,0,0,0,,No one will be able to stand against us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.49,0:13:35.48,2,,0,0,0,,Keep them locked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.26,0:13:37.82,2,,0,0,0,,After the harmonic convergence,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.29,0:13:39.63,2,,0,0,0,,I will come for Korra.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.75,0:13:41.78,2,,0,0,0,,Yes, father.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.25,0:13:47.76,2,,0,0,0,,I failed in every way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.00,0:13:50.44,2,,0,0,0,,We've lost Jinora forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.86,0:13:51.86,2,,0,0,0,,There's still a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.43,0:13:53.37,2,,0,0,0,,They didn't get Bumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.33,0:14:15.78,2,,0,0,0,,Oh, you want to play some more.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.18,0:14:17.56,2,,0,0,0,,Well, bring it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.71,0:14:46.73,2,,0,0,0,,Oh, we're playing dirty, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.36,0:15:15.60,2,,0,0,0,,Hmm, looks like we've got a music lover here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.95,0:15:27.79,2,,0,0,0,,Reinforcements!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.59,0:15:32.81,2,,0,0,0,,All right, soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.31,0:15:35.52,2,,0,0,0,,Looks like it's on us to save the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.84,0:15:37.52,2,,0,0,0,,Luckily, I've got a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.96,0:15:48.11,2,,0,0,0,,Eska, Desna, listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.80,0:15:50.41,2,,0,0,0,,You've got to help us stop Unalaq.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.01,0:15:54.13,2,,0,0,0,,I know he's your father, but Vaatu has made him completely crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.09,0:15:56.87,2,,0,0,0,,We will never turn on our father.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.49,0:15:58.16,2,,0,0,0,,Please,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.95,0:16:02.99,2,,0,0,0,,if you let me out now, I can still stop him from destroying everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.50,0:16:05.10,2,,0,0,0,,Once he fuses with Vaatu,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.48,0:16:06.94,2,,0,0,0,,no one will be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.82,0:16:10.30,2,,0,0,0,,Desna, he won't be your father anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.14,0:16:16.11,2,,0,0,0,,You don't know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.73,0:16:19.24,2,,0,0,0,,Our father is the wisest man in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.24,0:16:22.87,2,,0,0,0,,If he says what he is doing is right, I believe him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.59,0:16:42.93,2,,0,0,0,,You know, if I wanted some ball of evil lurking over my shoulder all the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.22,0:16:44.93,2,,0,0,0,,I'd have stayed home with my mother-in-law.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.11,0:16:51.88,2,,0,0,0,,All right, spirit army,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.04,0:16:55.99,2,,0,0,0,,your general is here. Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.12,0:17:04.63,2,,0,0,0,,It's working.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.85,0:17:14.31,2,,0,0,0,,It's not working.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.84,0:17:49.71,2,,0,0,0,,Get me out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.77,0:18:26.08,2,,0,0,0,,All right, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.30,0:18:27.63,2,,0,0,0,,Rescue time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.75,0:18:38.08,2,,0,0,0,,Bumi,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.46,0:18:41.82,2,,0,0,0,,how did you manage to take out this entire encampment on your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.53,0:18:44.56,2,,0,0,0,,I did it all with my trusty flute and...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.45,0:18:47.62,2,,0,0,0,,oh, never mind. You wouldn't believe it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.10,0:18:49.26,2,,0,0,0,,Let's get moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.29,0:19:04.68,2,,0,0,0,,You run into the portal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.51,0:19:07.73,2,,0,0,0,,I'll try to hold off anyone who comes after you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.15,0:19:10.25,2,,0,0,0,,No, you're too hurt. You need a healer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.48,0:19:14.28,2,,0,0,0,,Asami, can you take Oogi and my dad back to my mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.75,0:19:16.98,2,,0,0,0,,This is my fight now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.36,0:19:17.81,2,,0,0,0,,Korra.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.88,0:19:20.55,2,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.78,0:19:22.04,2,,0,0,0,,I love you too, dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.80,0:19:24.20,2,,0,0,0,,Yipyip.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.82,0:19:35.75,2,,0,0,0,,Once we're inside, you go find Jinora.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.30,0:19:38.11,2,,0,0,0,,Mako and Bolin will take care of Unalaq
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.34,0:19:40.54,2,,0,0,0,,while I close the portal, so Vaatu can't escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.11,0:19:42.63,2,,0,0,0,,Wait a second. Worst-case scenario.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.91,0:19:44.86,2,,0,0,0,,So we're fighting Unalaq, you close the portals,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.86,0:19:47.45,2,,0,0,0,,and let's just say something happens to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.17,0:19:50.35,2,,0,0,0,,Are we gonna be trapped in there for eternity?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.62,0:19:55.85,2,,0,0,0,,If everything goes as planned, we'll all walk out together after harmonic convergence.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.12,0:19:57.69,2,,0,0,0,,If not...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.31,0:20:05.80,2,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.02,0:20:33.49,2,,0,0,0,,Tenzin, go find Jinora.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.19,0:20:35.68,2,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.46,0:21:30.08,2,,0,0,0,,You're running out of time, Raava.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.51,0:21:33.13,2,,0,0,0,,I know you feel it coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.41,0:22:55.94,2,,0,0,0,,[Laughing maniacally]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.94,0:01:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,这件外套是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.88,0:01:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,还有，你从哪儿搞到的馅饼？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.06,0:01:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这是瓦里克的船，你永远不知道你会发现什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.90,0:01:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这里有一整层都摆满了哈哈镜的船舱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.32,0:01:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,还有一层甲板全都是猫鳄
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.98,0:01:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我想念那个家伙了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.43,0:01:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,他真的知道怎么让漫漫旅途变得充满乐趣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.25,0:01:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那么，你告诉科拉了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.25,0:01:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,关于你们分手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.09,0:01:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,然后在她被暗灵攻击时你又跟麻美约会什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.77,0:01:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你能小点声吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.19,0:01:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我在等合适的时机
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.53,0:01:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.23,0:02:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,有个聪明人曾经说过，告诉女朋友坏消息
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.38,0:02:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,就像撕掉一个吸血水蛭，你只需要动作快点并了结它
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.09,0:02:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我真讨厌你听我话的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.08,0:02:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.44,0:02:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,吴纳克知道你会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.02,0:02:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你必须用上全部神通之力去阻止他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.76,0:02:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我会关闭灵界通道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.61,0:02:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,把瓦图再关上个一万年
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.11,0:02:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,然后让吴纳克后悔自己出生于世
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.19,0:02:30.19,5,,0,0,0,,Nice Battleship！！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.14,0:02:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你，信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.24,0:02:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你想说什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.35,0:02:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不不，没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.16,0:02:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,等我们一到达南极水族部落
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.78,0:02:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我们首先要冲破主要港口的封锁线
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.27,0:02:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我们就可以和托纳克以及他的部队集结
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.91,0:03:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,击垮守卫通道的防御力量，之后进入灵界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.84,0:03:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,哇，什么时候开始我的弟弟想要击垮破坏东西了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.44,0:03:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我会不惜一切来拯救我女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.21,0:03:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都想去救吉诺拉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.44,0:03:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,但我觉得你的计划可能有一点太过于激进了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.45,0:03:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,要知道我们只有七个人和一艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.04,0:03:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.13,0:03:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那么你有什么建议？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.29,0:03:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,像这样的进攻要讲究策略
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.46,0:03:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我记得有次我在一个风暴海峡被海盗们团团围住
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.97,0:03:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我们最后仅凭一根羽毛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.80,0:03:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,两个鸡蛋和一桶糖浆就将他们尽数捕获
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.97,0:03:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,在我不想再听到你的任何鬼扯了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.61,0:03:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这是很严肃的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.19,0:03:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我们快到了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.33,0:03:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,就快了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.75,0:03:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.66,0:03:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚刚从南方部队收到一个不好的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.97,0:03:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.30,0:04:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.78,0:04:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里见到你真高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.86,0:04:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,父亲在哪儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.89,0:04:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,吴纳克荡平了南水部队的所有抵抗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.63,0:04:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,并且抓到了你父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.19,0:04:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我会把他救回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.28,0:04:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我母亲在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.19,0:04:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,她在治疗房里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.74,0:04:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,伤员太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.41,0:04:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.53,0:04:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,她的灵魂被困在灵界了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.08,0:04:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，我的天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.70,0:04:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,她已经去了多久了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.49,0:04:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,将近一周
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.04,0:04:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直试着让她的能量保持流动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.89,0:04:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,但我能感觉到她在不断远离我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.92,0:04:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,母亲，现在只有你能救她了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.54,0:04:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,她这样还能再存活多久
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.01,0:05:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.40,0:05:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,但她能坚持这么久已经很厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.37,0:05:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我和反抗者谈过了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.61,0:05:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,他们说吴纳克把南极通道团团围住了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.56,0:05:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,离谐波汇聚只有几个小时了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.86,0:05:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那么现在我们只能自己去打破敌人的防线，然后进入通道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.86,0:05:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,没有必要再继续讨论了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.42,0:05:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经明白任务是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.13,0:05:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,自杀式行动吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.39,0:05:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,要知道，我曾经遇到过类似的情形
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.97,0:05:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我的排要在没有水的情况下在一周内爬过沙漠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.71,0:05:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,但当我们终于找到一百里内唯一的绿洲时
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.50,0:05:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,它却被愤怒的沙宗包围着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.53,0:05:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我意识到我们唯一靠近水源的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.80,0:05:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,是从上空降落
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.24,0:05:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我制作了一个弹射器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.25,0:05:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,在几只训练有素的猪猴的帮助下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.85,0:05:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不要再说你那荒谬的胡话了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.98,0:05:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你没发现整个世界的命运和吉诺拉的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.74,0:05:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,都取决于我们今天所做之事了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.95,0:05:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,等等，也许布米说的对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.21,0:06:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我们没有弹射器和猪猴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.06,0:06:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我们有一只飞天野牛，而且瓦里克的船上有一架飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.60,0:06:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,没准我们就能从上空进攻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.52,0:06:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你的想法是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.58,0:06:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,信，波林和我用飞机来分散注意力，打散一些防御力量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.34,0:06:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你，丹增，布米和凯娅乘坐无忌找开口进入灵界通道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.44,0:06:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我们行动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.83,0:06:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还留在这里做什么，父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.24,0:06:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,入侵行动完全成功
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.91,0:06:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,南水部落在我们掌控之下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.41,0:06:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,灵界通道已经打开
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.33,0:06:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你已经恢复了平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.00,0:06:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我们想要回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.87,0:06:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你们不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.92,0:06:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我迄今完成的每件事，与我将要完成之事相比都会黯然失色
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.15,0:07:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,还要做什么？水族部落已经合并了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.27,0:07:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,从今往后，这里将再没有水族部落
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.95,0:07:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,没有种族和国家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.37,0:07:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,世界将会转变成无比壮观又崭新的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.49,0:07:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,而我将会领导这场华丽的革命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.73,0:07:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,现在出去让部队做好守卫灵界通道的准备
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.96,0:07:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,防御谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.35,0:07:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经打败了所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.27,0:07:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,神通很快就要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.37,0:07:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,她没别的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.02,0:07:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.23,0:07:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我是一个被固定在上百尺高空的机翼上的御土师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.37,0:07:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,所以没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.38,0:07:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,别担心，他们万万不会预料到这招的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.26,0:08:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我想他们预料到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.82,0:08:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,麻美
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.66,0:08:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,做好准备
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.78,0:08:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,开火
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.57,0:09:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这里到处都是神灵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.46,0:09:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我看不到一个开口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.26,0:09:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我们盘旋一周看看是不是能想办法从另一侧进入
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.02,0:09:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,坚持住
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.38,0:09:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这些神灵在把无忌往下拽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.14,0:09:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我们正在下降
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.00,0:09:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,快从它身上下去，你这个粘人又恶心的小黏球
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.58,0:09:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我要是掉下去了，你也得和我一起下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.87,0:09:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,布米
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.84,0:10:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望瓦里克能把这段拍成电影
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.15,0:10:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,就起名叫《纳塔克：天空战士》
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.96,0:10:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,防撞姿势！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.92,0:11:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.02,0:11:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,科拉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.53,0:11:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.47,0:11:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我辜负了你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.73,0:11:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不要放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.08,0:11:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,谐波汇聚还没有到来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.71,0:11:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还有机会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.63,0:11:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我们尽力了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.65,0:12:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,大家伙儿，恭喜了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.76,0:12:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你们都坐上了来观看世界新秩序开端的前排座位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.94,0:12:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你不知道你在干什么，吴纳克
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.54,0:12:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,释放瓦图不会让你变得强大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.55,0:12:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,它只会让你成为过去一万年中所有美好事物的叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.75,0:12:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你认为神通万做的事情是好的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.57,0:12:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,从人界驱逐了几乎全部神灵？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.44,0:12:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,降世神通从没有带来过和平，只有混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.06,0:12:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你把自己称作两个世界的桥梁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.10,0:12:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,但这里本就不应该有桥梁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.72,0:12:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,人类和神灵应该共存
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.62,0:12:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,就算瓦图逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.77,0:12:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我也会把他关回他的牢狱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.03,0:12:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,就像万做的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.49,0:12:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,的确当万和拉瓦合为一体时，他帮她获得了优势
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.08,0:12:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,但这一次，我会来维持决斗的平等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.37,0:12:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,当谐波汇聚到来时，我会与瓦图合二为一
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.96,0:12:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我们将会一同成为新的降世神通
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.00,0:12:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,暗黑逆神通
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.79,0:12:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你的时代结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.41,0:13:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好好想想你的所作所为
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.11,0:13:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你一直都与神灵有着很深的联系
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.16,0:13:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,但你仍旧是一个人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.74,0:13:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你仍然是我的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.70,0:13:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你是爱丝卡和杰斯纳的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.15,0:13:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你愿意抛弃你的人性，变成一个妖魔吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.56,0:13:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会比你自己的女儿更像一个妖魔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.71,0:13:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,唯一的区别就是，她无法认识她自己的灵力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.07,0:13:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我却能把自己和灵力完全结合
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.81,0:13:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,瓦图和我会化为一体
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.01,0:13:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,没有人可以抵抗我们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.49,0:13:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,继续关着他们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.26,0:13:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,等谐波汇聚之后
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.29,0:13:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我会回来找科拉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.75,0:13:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,遵命，父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.25,0:13:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我完全失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.00,0:13:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我们永远失去吉诺拉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.86,0:13:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还有一个机会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.43,0:13:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,他们没抓到布米
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.33,0:14:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，你还想再找点乐子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.18,0:14:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊，来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.71,0:14:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，我们玩阴的，是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.36,0:15:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,看来我们这儿有个音乐爱好者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.95,0:15:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,援军
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.59,0:15:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好的，士兵们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.31,0:15:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,看来这次到我们来拯救世界了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.84,0:15:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,幸运的是，我有个计划
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.96,0:15:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,爱丝卡，杰斯纳，听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.80,0:15:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你们一定要帮我阻止吴纳克
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.01,0:15:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道他是你们的爸爸，但是瓦图已经让他完全疯狂了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.09,0:15:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我们绝对不会背叛父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.49,0:15:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.95,0:16:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你现在放我出去，我仍旧可以阻止他摧毁一切
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.50,0:16:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦他和瓦图融合了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.48,0:16:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,没有人能够幸免
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.82,0:16:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,杰斯纳，他不再会是你的父亲了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.14,0:16:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你根本不明白你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.73,0:16:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我们父亲是这个世界上最睿智的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.24,0:16:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他说他做的是对的，我就相信他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.59,0:16:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道，如果要让这群邪恶的家伙一直在我周围转悠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.22,0:16:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我宁可陪我岳母大人呆在家里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.11,0:16:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,好了，神灵部队
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.04,0:16:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你们的将军在这里，跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.12,0:17:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这招奏效了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.85,0:17:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,没奏效
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.84,0:17:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,放我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.77,0:18:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好了，伙计们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.30,0:18:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我来救你们啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.75,0:18:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,布米
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.46,0:18:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你是怎么一个人干掉整个营地的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.53,0:18:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我是与我可靠的笛子一起，还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.45,0:18:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，算了，反正你是不会相信的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.10,0:18:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我们该动身了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.29,0:19:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你们进入通道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.51,0:19:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我会尽力拖住任何想要追你们的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.15,0:19:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，你受伤太严重了，你需要一个水疗师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.48,0:19:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,麻美，你能带无忌和我父亲回我母亲那里去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.75,0:19:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,从现在起就是我的战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.36,0:19:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,科拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.88,0:19:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.78,0:19:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我也爱你，父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.80,0:19:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,驾，驾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.82,0:19:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一旦进去后，你们去找吉诺拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.30,0:19:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,当我关闭通道时
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.34,0:19:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,信和波林来对付吴纳克，这样瓦图就无法逃脱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.11,0:19:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下，如果发生最坏的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.91,0:19:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我们和吴纳克作战，你关闭通道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.86,0:19:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,就比方说你发生了什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.17,0:19:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是不是就永远被困在那里了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.62,0:19:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,如果一切按照计划的进行，我们会在谐波汇聚之后一起出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.12,0:19:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不行……
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.31,0:20:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我们出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.02,0:20:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,丹增，快去找吉诺拉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.19,0:20:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.46,0:21:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你的时间越来越少了，拉瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.51,0:21:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你能感到它的到来
